headline: Countree Food Takes Key Role at World Processed Deciduous Fruit Conference (CANCON16)
summary: QINGDAO, China, Oct. 10, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The 16th World Processed Deciduous Fruit Conference (CANCON16), the largest and most influential international event for the canned fruit industry, recently concluded with discussions on the future challenges and innovations shaping the sector. The conference drew industry leaders, processors, and growers from major producing nations like the USA, Chile, Argentina, South Africa, and various European countries.
